      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure? This car is in great shape and has been super dependable for me. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how much fun it is to drive!",
