    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2008 Porsche Cayman S, featuring the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six power plant equipped with VarioCam Plus. This mid-engine platform delivers exceptional balance and a low polar moment of inertia, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The naturally aspirated boxer engine pulls cleanly through the rev range, benefiting from a recent Air-Oil Separator (AOS) replacement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing McPherson struts at all four corners for precise turn-in and communicative hydraulic steering feedback. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are Excellent. This is a driver-centric example optimized for lateral G-loading and throttle-steer adjustability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
