    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and meticulous care. The exterior finish maintains a deep, mirror-like luster, with only a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door that are barely noticeable. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the premium leather upholstery is soft and intact, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, operate perfectly. Mechanically, this car is solid and dependable. It has a full service history, with the most recent major maintenance performed just 2,000 miles ago, including new brake pads and a fresh set of high-performance tires. The engine idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. This is a turn-key vehicle that has been garage-kept and loved, ready for a new owner who appreciates a car that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
